videos.description: Maryland guard Anthony Cowan Jr. gets caught in the lane but fakes the pass and finds himself open for the easy floater.
videos.headline: Cowan Jr. fakes the pass then puts in the floater

videos.description: Ohio State's Andre Wesson gets out in transition and flushes the two-handed reverse dunk.
videos.headline: OSU's Andre Wesson takes flight with reverse dunk

videos.description: Andre Wesson is stuffed at the rim but it ends up with Duane Washington Jr., who knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: OSU's Washington Jr. knocks down 3 after Maryland block
